│ **I. Campaign Overview**                                                                                               │
│                                                                                                                        │
│ *   **Campaign Name:** EcoClean - Millennial Spring Cleaning                                                           │
│ *   **Campaign Goal:** Drive online sales of EcoClean cleaning product starter kits.                                   │
│ *   **Target Audience:** Environmentally conscious Millennials (28-35 years old), living in urban areas, active on     │
│ social media (Instagram, Pinterest), concerned about plastic waste, and willing to spend slightly more for sustainable │
│ products. They value brands that are transparent about their ingredients and ethical practices. They are often renters │
│ or first-time homeowners.                                                                                              │
│ *   **Products/Services:** EcoClean Starter Kit (includes all-purpose cleaner concentrate, laundry detergent sheets,   │
│ and dish soap bar).                                                                                                    │
│ *   **Unique Selling Proposition (USP):** EcoClean offers ultra-concentrated, plant-based cleaning solutions that      │
│ drastically reduce plastic waste compared to traditional cleaning products. Our products are cruelty-free, vegan, and  │
│ shipped in recycled packaging. For every kit purchased, we donate to ocean cleanup initiatives.                        │
│ *   **Budget:** $2400                                                                                                  │
│ *   **Campaign Duration:** April 1st - June 30th                                                                       │
│ *   **Geographic Targeting:** United States (targeting the top 20 most populous metropolitan areas)                    │
